               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡ ኢየሱስ፡. Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Saint George zä-Säläda Mogäs, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ።; Hymn to Saint George, “O who is quick for help,” ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡; Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡</summary>
